== 開發 ==
2013年9月，NBC購買了本劇版權。<ref>{{cite web|last=Ausiello|first=Michael|title=Scoop: NBC Snags Katherine Heigl CIA Drama|url=http://tvline.com/2013/09/09/katherine-heigl-cia-drama-nbc-2014/|work=[[TVLine|TVLine]]|accessdate=2014-05-07|date=2013-09-09|archive-date=2014-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140226215236/http://tvline.com/2013/09/09/katherine-heigl-cia-drama-nbc-2014/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年1月，電視網宣布獲得了試播集的製作預訂。<ref>{{cite web|last=Snierson|first=Dan|title=NBC pilots: Drama starring Katherine Heigl, comedy produced by Amy Poehler|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/01/19/nbc-pilots-katherine-heigl-amy-poehler/|work=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|accessdate=2014-05-07|date=2014-01-19|archive-date=2014-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140327222023/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/01/19/nbc-pilots-katherine-heigl-amy-poehler/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2014年5月，試播集正式被預訂。<ref>{{cite web|last=Friedlander|first=Whitney|title=NBC Orders Katherine Heigl CIA Drama to Series|url=http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/katherine-heigl-cia-drama-nbc-1201173637/|work=[[Variety_(magazine){{!}}Variety|Variety (magazine){{!}}Variety]]|accessdate=2014-05-07|date=2014-05-06|archive-date=2014-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140507013530/http://variety.com/2014/tv/news/katherine-heigl-cia-drama-nbc-1201173637/|dead-url=no}}</ref>2014年8月，總監制{{link-en|艾德·布蘭諾|Ed Bernero}}於首播前離開劇組，原因是與執行製作喬伊·康納翰的製作理念不一。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Hibberd|first1=James|title=Katherine Heigl's new drama 'State of Affairs' losing showrunner|url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/katherine-heigl-showrunner-state-of-affairs/|website=[[娛樂周刊|娛樂周刊]]|accessdate=2014-08-16|date=2014-08-15|archive-date=2014-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140816003245/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/katherine-heigl-showrunner-state-of-affairs/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

